'''植物病毒'''（Plant virus）泛指感染[[植物|植物]]的[[病毒|病毒]]，大多為[[正單鏈RNA病毒|正單鏈RNA病毒]]<ref name="pmid28154139">{{cite journal| author=Hyodo K, Hashimoto K, Kuchitsu K, Suzuki N, Okuno T| title=Harnessing host ROS-generating machinery for the robust genome replication of a plant RNA virus. | journal=Proc Natl Acad Sci U S A | year= 2017 | volume= 114 | issue= 7 | pages= E1282-E1290 | pmid=28154139 | doi=10.1073/pnas.1610212114 | pmc=5320965 | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=28154139  }} </ref>，一般不具有[[病毒包膜|外膜]]（[[布尼亞病毒目|布尼亞病毒目]]與[[單股反鏈病毒目|單股反鏈病毒目]]的病毒則有）<ref name="pmid31275344">{{cite journal| author=Ibrahim A, Odon V, Kormelink R| title=Plant Viruses in Plant Molecular Pharming: Toward the Use of Enveloped Viruses. | journal=Front Plant Sci | year= 2019 | volume= 10 | issue=  | pages= 803 | pmid=31275344 | doi=10.3389/fpls.2019.00803 | pmc=6594412 | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=31275344  }} </ref>，有許多外觀呈棒状<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The good viruses: viral mutualistic symbioses|last=Roossinck|first=M. J.|journal=Nature Reviews Microbiology|issue=2|doi=10.1038/nrmicro2491|year=2011|volume=9|pages=99–108|pmid=21200397}}</ref>，也有呈正多面體者，其中{{le|雙生病毒科|Geminiviridae}}的病毒由雙生的兩個正二十面體組成。植物病毒在自然界中大多以動物媒介、[[花粉|花粉]]或[[種子|種子]]傳播，較少如{{le|動物病毒|animal virus}}般以直接接觸傳染，動物媒介包括[[昆蟲|昆蟲]]、[[線蟲|線蟲]]與[[蛛形綱|蜘蛛]]等，其中以昆蟲居多（特別是[[半翅目|半翅目]]昆蟲），有些病毒可進入昆蟲的血腔中，使其終生具備散播病毒的能力，有些病毒並可影響宿主花朵的特性以吸引或阻止昆蟲前來<ref name="pmid31312033"/>。植物可以[[植物激素|植物激素]]（[[水楊酸|水楊酸]]、[[茉莉酸|茉莉酸]]與[[脫落酸|脫落酸]]等<ref name="pmid33630970">{{cite journal| author=Zhao S, Li Y| title=Current understanding of the interplays between host hormones and plant viral infections. | journal=PLoS Pathog | year= 2021 | volume= 17 | issue= 2 | pages= e1009242 | pmid=33630970 | doi=10.1371/journal.ppat.1009242 | pmc=7906326 | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=33630970  }} </ref>）啟動抗病毒反應，並以[[RNA干擾|RNA干擾]]等機制清除病毒RNA<ref name="Blevins">{{cite journal | vauthors = Blevins T, Rajeswaran R, Shivaprasad PV, Beknazariants D, Si-Ammour A, Park HS, Vazquez F, Robertson D, Meins F, Hohn T, Pooggin MM | title = Four plant Dicers mediate viral small RNA biogenesis and DNA virus induced silencing | journal = Nucleic Acids Research | volume = 34 | issue = 21 | pages = 6233–46 | year = 2006 | pmid = 17090584 | pmc = 1669714 | doi = 10.1093/nar/gkl886}}</ref>，而病毒也有許多機制對抗宿主免疫反應，例如形成膜結構以避免被宿主核酸酶切割<ref name="pmid28154139"/>，並可利用植物透過[[原生質絲|原生質絲]]在細胞間傳遞[[mRNA|mRNA]]的機制傳播自己的RNA<ref name="Plasmodesmata">{{cite journal|author=Oparka KJ, Alison GR|title= Plasmodesmata. A Not So Open-and-Shut Case|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_plant-physiology_2001-01_125_1/page/123|journal= Plant Physiology|year=2001|volume= 125|page=123–126}}</ref>。

許多糧食作物與經濟作物可被植物病毒感染<ref name="pmid31283443">{{cite journal| author=Jones RAC, Naidu RA| title=Global Dimensions of Plant Virus Diseases: Current Status and Future Perspectives. | journal=Annu Rev Virol | year= 2019 | volume= 6 | issue= 1 | pages= 387-409 | pmid=31283443 | doi=10.1146/annurev-virology-092818-015606 | pmc= | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=31283443  }} </ref>，如{{le|玉米褪绿斑驳病毒|Maize lethal necrosis disease}}、{{le|大麥黃矮病毒|barley yellow dwarf virus}}、{{le|小麦线条花叶病毒|Wheat streak mosaic virus}}、{{le|水稻东格鲁病毒|Tungrovirus}}、{{le|馬鈴薯Y病毒|Potato virus Y}}、[[甘薯褪绿矮化病毒|甘薯褪绿矮化病毒]]（sweet potato chlorotic stunt virus）、{{le|番茄褐色皱果病毒|Tomato brown rugose fruit virus}}、{{le|胡瓜綠斑嵌紋病毒|Cucumber green mottle mosaic virus}}等，可能影響[[糧食安全|糧食安全]]<ref name="pmid33504044">{{cite journal| author=Jones RAC| title=Global Plant Virus Disease Pandemics and Epidemics. | journal=Plants (Basel) | year= 2021 | volume= 10 | issue= 2 | pages=  | pmid=33504044 | doi=10.3390/plants10020233 | pmc=7911862 | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=33504044  }} </ref>，估計每年在全世界造成超過600億美元的經濟損失<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2019/07/190717142645.htm|title=Plant viruses may be reshaping our world|publisher=Science Daily|date=2019-07-17|access-date=2021-04-27|archive-date=2021-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210605173043/https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2019/07/190717142645.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，不過許多植物病毒的感染並不造成任何症狀，甚至可與植物[[互利共生|互利共生]]，例如{{le|圓葉菸草 |Nicotiana benthamiana}}被許多病毒感染後可提升對缺水逆境的抗性；有些植物還可將病毒的基因用作其他功能，如[[白三叶草潜隐病毒|白三叶草潜隐病毒]]（clover cryptic virus）的衣殼蛋白被一些植物用於抑制{{le|根瘤|Root nodule}}的形成<ref name="pmid21200397">{{cite journal| author=Roossinck MJ| title=The good viruses: viral mutualistic symbioses. | journal=Nat Rev Microbiol | year= 2011 | volume= 9 | issue= 2 | pages= 99-108 | pmid=21200397 | doi=10.1038/nrmicro2491 | pmc= | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=21200397  }} </ref>。

歷史上第一種被發現的病毒[[菸草鑲嵌病毒|菸草鑲嵌病毒]]（TMV）即為植物病毒<ref name="pmid11570281">{{cite journal| author=Lecoq H| title=[Discovery of the first virus, the tobacco mosaic virus: 1892 or 1898?]. | journal=C R Acad Sci III | year= 2001 | volume= 324 | issue= 10 | pages= 929-33 | pmid=11570281 | doi=10.1016/s0764-4469(01)01368-3 | pmc= | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=11570281 |language=fr }} </ref>。有些植物病毒在科學研究或農業上具有應用價值，在生物學研究中，有些植物病毒可被研究人員用作[[病毒載體|載體]]將遺傳物質送入植物細胞中<ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Abrahamian|first1=Peter|last2=Hammond|first2=Rosemarie W.|last3=Hammond|first3=John|date=2020-06-10|title=Plant Virus-Derived Vectors: Applications in Agricultural and Medical Biotechnology|journal=Annual Review of Virology|volume=7|doi=10.1146/annurev-virology-010720-054958|issn=2327-0578|pmid=32520661}}</ref>；有些[[園藝植物|園藝植物]]被病毒感染可提升其價值，如十七世紀荷蘭的[[鬱金香狂熱|鬱金香狂熱]]中，被[[鬱金香條斑病毒|鬱金香條斑病毒]]感染的[[鬱金香|鬱金香]]花朵上有不同顏色的條紋，因此價格非常高昂<ref>{{cite journal|author=Garber, Peter M.|title=Tulipmania|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-political-economy_1989-06_97_3/page/535|journal= Journal of Political Economy|volume= 97|issue= 3|year= 1989|page=535-560}}</ref>；有些植物病毒則因能殺傷[[雜草|雜草]]或害蟲而可用於[[生物防治|生物防治]]<ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Harding|first1=Dylan P.|last2=Raizada|first2=Manish N.|date=2015|title=Controlling weeds with fungi, bacteria and viruses: a review|journal=Frontiers in Plant Science|volume=6|pages=659|doi=10.3389/fpls.2015.00659|issn=1664-462X|pmc=4551831|pmid=26379687}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Bonning|first1=Bryony C.|last2=Pal|first2=Narinder|last3=Liu|first3=Sijun|last4=Wang|first4=Zhaohui|last5=Sivakumar|first5=S.|last6=Dixon|first6=Philip M.|last7=King|first7=Glenn F.|last8=Miller|first8=W. Allen|date=January 2014|title=Toxin delivery by the coat protein of an aphid-vectored plant virus provides plant resistance to aphids|journal=Nature Biotechnology|volume=32|issue=1|pages=102–105|doi=10.1038/nbt.2753|issn=1546-1696|pmid=24316580}}</ref>。

==分類==
有約30個[[科_(生物)|科]]的病毒可感染植物，其中有些科的病毒皆為植物病毒，有些則包含感染動物、真菌等其他生物的病毒。許多植物病毒與[[真菌病毒|真菌病毒]]或感染[[節肢動物|節肢動物]]的病毒關係接近，有些植物病毒可在真菌細胞內複製，也有些真菌病毒可在植物細胞內複製，此現象可能與陸生植物和真菌的共生關係有關<ref name="pmid31312033">{{cite journal| author=Lefeuvre P, Martin DP, Elena SF, Shepherd DN, Roumagnac P, Varsani A| title=Evolution and ecology of plant viruses. | journal=Nat Rev Microbiol | year= 2019 | volume= 17 | issue= 10 | pages= 632-644 | pmid=31312033 | doi=10.1038/s41579-019-0232-3 | pmc= | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=31312033  }} </ref>。
